ss=\"sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-border/80 bg-background/85 backdrop-blur-md\"><div class=\"container-af flex h-14 items-center justify-between gap-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 font-bold tracking-tight\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"inline-flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-primary text-primary-foreground text-xs font-black\">AF</span><span class=\"hidden sm:inline\">AlgoForge</span></a><nav class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-1\" aria-label=\"Main\"><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/problems\">Problems</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/topics\">Topics</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/patterns\">Patterns</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/roadmaps\">Roadmaps</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/blind-75\">Blind 75</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/companies\">Companies</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></nav></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"hidden sm:inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:border-primary/40 transition-colors\" href=\"/search\"><span>Search…</span><kbd class=\"rounded border border-border bg-muted px-1.5 text-[10px] font-mono\">/</kbd></a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/dashboard\">Progress</a><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 hover:bg-muted text-foreground h-9 w-9\" aria-label=\"Toggle theme\"></button></div></div></header><main id=\"main\" class=\"min-h-[70vh]\"><div class=\"container-af py-10\"><nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Problems\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/problems\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Minimum Operations to Remove Adjacent Ones in Matrix\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/problems/minimum-operations-to-remove-adjacent-ones-in-matrix\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":4,\"name\":\"C++\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/problems/minimum-operations-to-remove-adjacent-ones-in-matrix/cpp\"}]}</script><ol class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1.5\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-border\">/</span><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/problems\">Problems</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-border\">/</span><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/problems/minimum-operations-to-remove-adjacent-ones-in-matrix\">Minimum Operations to Remove Adjacent Ones in Matrix</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-border\">/</span><span class=\"text-foreground font-medium\" aria-current=\"page\">C++</span></li></ol></nav><div class=\"mt-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide bg-hard/15 text-hard\">Hard</span></div><h1 class=\"mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Minimum Operations to Remove Adjacent Ones in Matrix<!-- --> — <!-- -->C++</h1><p class=\"mt-2 text-muted-foreground\"><a class=\"text-primary hover:underline\" href=\"/problems/minimum-operations-to-remove-adjacent-ones-in-matrix\">Full explanation</a> · <!-- -->Time <!-- -->O(m * n * sqrt(m * n))<!-- --> · Space <!-- -->O(m + n)</p><div class=\"mt-8\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border overflow-hidden bg-code-bg text-slate-100\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2 border-b border-white/10 bg-black/30 px-2 py-1.5\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-1\" role=\"tablist\" aria-label=\"Language\"><button role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium transition-colors bg-white/15 text-white\">C++</button><button role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium transition-colors text-slate-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5\">Python</button></div><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 px-3 text-sm text-slate-300 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/10 h-8\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Copy code\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-copy h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"14\" x=\"8\" y=\"8\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2\"></path></svg>Copy</button></div><pre class=\"overflow-x-auto p-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed font-mono max-h-[32rem]\"><code>// Time:  O(m * n * sqrt(m + n))\n// Space: O(m * n)\n\n// template from https://github.com/kth-competitive-programming/kactl/blob/main/content/graph/hopcroftKarp.h\nbool dfs(int a, int L, vector&lt;vector&lt;int&gt;&gt;&amp; g, vector&lt;int&gt;&amp; btoa, vector&lt;int&gt;&amp; A, vector&lt;int&gt;&amp; B) {\n    if (A[a] != L) return 0;\n    A[a] = -1;\n    for (int b : g[a]) if (B[b] == L + 1) {\n        B[b] = 0;\n        if (btoa[b] == -1 || dfs(btoa[b], L + 1, g, btoa, A, B))\n            return btoa[b] = a, 1;\n    }\n    return 0;\n}\n\nint hopcroftKarp(vector&lt;vector&lt;int&gt;&gt;&amp; g, vector&lt;int&gt;&amp; btoa) {\n    int res = 0;\n    vector&lt;int&gt; A(g.size()), B(btoa.size()), cur, next;\n    for (;;) {\n        fill(begin(A), end(A), 0);\n        fill(begin(B), end(B), 0);\n        /// Find the starting nodes for BFS (i.e. layer 0).\n        cur.clear();\n        for (int a : btoa) if(a != -1) A[a] = -1;\n        for (int a = 0; a &lt; size(g); ++a) if(A[a] == 0) cur.push_back(a);\n        /// Find all layers using bfs.\n        for (int lay = 1;; lay++) {\n            bool islast = 0;\n            next.clear();\n            for (int a : cur) for (int b : g[a]) {\n                if (btoa[b] == -1) {\n                    B[b] = lay;\n                    islast = 1;\n                }\n                else if (btoa[b] != a &amp;&amp; !B[b]) {\n                    B[b] = lay;\n                    next.push_back(btoa[b]);\n                }\n            }\n            if (islast) break;\n            if (next.empty()) return res;\n            for (int a : next) A[a] = lay;\n            cur.swap(next);\n        }\n        /// Use DFS to scan for augmenting paths.\n        for (int a = 0; a &lt; size(g); ++a)\n            res += dfs(a, 0, g, btoa, A, B);\n    }\n}\n\nclass Solution {\npublic:\n    int minimumOperations(vector&lt;vector&lt;int&gt;&gt;&amp; grid) {\n        vector&lt;vector&lt;int&gt;&gt; adj;\n        vector&lt;unordered_map&lt;int, int&gt;&gt; ids(2);\n        vector&lt;vector&lt;bool&gt;&gt; lookup(size(grid), vector&lt;bool&gt;(size(grid[0])));\n        for (int i = 0; i &lt; size(grid); ++i) {\n            for (int j = 0; j &lt; size(grid[0]); ++j) {\n                if (!grid[i][j]) {\n                    continue;\n                }\n                iter_dfs(grid, i, j, &amp;lookup, &amp;ids, &amp;adj);\n            }\n        }\n        vector&lt;int&gt; b(size(ids[1]), -1);\n        return hopcroftKarp(adj, b);\n    }\n\nprivate:\n    void iter_dfs(const vector&lt;vector&lt;int&gt;&gt;&amp; grid, int i, int j,\n                  vector&lt;vector&lt;bool&gt;&gt; *lookup,\n                  vector&lt;unordered_map&lt;int, int&gt;&gt; *ids,\n                  vector&lt;vector&lt;int&gt;&gt; *adj) {\n        static const vector&lt;pair&lt;int, int&gt;&gt; directions{{0, 1}, {1, 0}, {0, -1}, {-1, 0}};\n\n        if ((*lookup)[i][j]) {\n            return;\n        }\n        auto get_id = [&amp;grid, &amp;ids](int i, int j, int color) {\n            const int x = size(grid[0]) * i + j;\n            if (!(*ids)[color].count(x)) {\n                (*ids)[color][x] = size((*ids)[color]);\n            }\n            return (*ids)[color][x];\n        };\n\n        (*lookup)[i][j] = true;\n        vector&lt;tuple&lt;int, int, int&gt;&gt; stk = {{i, j, (i + j) % 2}};\n        while (!empty(stk)) {\n            const auto [i, j, color] = stk.back(); stk.pop_back();\n            for (const auto&amp; [di, dj] : directions) {\n                const int ni = i + di, nj = j + dj;\n                if (!(0 &lt;= ni &amp;&amp; ni &lt; size(grid) &amp;&amp;\n                      0 &lt;= nj &amp;&amp; nj &lt; size(grid[0]) &amp;&amp;\n                      grid[ni][nj])) {\n                    continue;\n                }\n                if (!color) {\n                    const int x = get_id(i, j, color);\n                    const int y = get_id(ni, nj, color ^ 1);\n                    adj-&gt;resize(size((*ids)[0]));\n                    (*adj)[x].emplace_back(y);\n                }\n                if ((*lookup)[ni][nj]) {\n                    continue;\n                }\n                (*lookup)[ni][nj] = true;\n                stk.emplace_back(ni, nj, color ^ 1);\n            }\n        }\n    }\n};\n</code></pre></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"mt-20 border-t border-border bg-sidebar\"><div class=\"container-af py-12 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4\"><div><p class=\"font-bold text-lg\">AlgoForge</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground max-w-xs\">Master coding interviews with patterns, roadmaps, and solutions</p></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm mb-3\">Learn</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/problems\">Problems</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/patterns\">Patterns</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/roadmaps\">Roadmaps</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/blind-75\">Blind 75</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/grind-169\">Grind 169</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm mb-3\">Interview</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/companies\">Companies</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/interview-preparation\">Interview prep</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/system-design\">System design</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/glossary\">Glossary</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm mb-3\">Product</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/pricing\">Pricing</a></li><li><a class=\